## Performance Rules

- Memoize expensive renders with `useMemo` and `React.memo` only after profiling
- The message list must use virtual scrolling if > 200 messages (`react-virtual`)
- SSE token events fire frequently during streaming — `appendToken` must not re-render the entire message list
- Lazy-load non-critical panels: `React.lazy()` + `Suspense` for Memory Viewer, Log Viewer, Settings
